; Coverage test for times.cc
; Exercise period dump with no duration (just a date range)
; This hits the "if (!duration) break" path in dump()

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food            $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test period "since 2024/01/01 until 2024/12/31"
--- Period expression tokens ---
TOK_SINCE: since
TOK_DATE:  year 2024 month Jan day 1
TOK_UNTIL: until
TOK_DATE:  year 2024 month Dec day 31
END_REACHED: <EOF>

--- Before stabilization ---
   range: from year 2024 month Jan day 1 to year 2024 month Dec day 31

--- After stabilization ---
   range: from year 2024 month Jan day 1 to year 2024 month Dec day 31
   start: 24-Jan-01
  finish: 24-Dec-31

--- Sample dates in range (max. 20) ---
 1: 24-Jan-01
end test
